title: [Vornavian Coast, Forest Road]
description: The road forks to the northeast and southeast here, and continues along the lake to the west.  The path to the southeast is nearly overgrown, and clearly not often traveled.  To the west, the woods thin out a bit, allowing more moonlight to the forest floor.
